{"tid":2323661,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"警阻靠近「送車師」照追嗌加油","createTime":"2020-12-13T10:36:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-13T12:30:20.000Z","uid":25558,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"0f052fe7678b3d9c4f84177e9759647d42ff25ce","tid":2323661,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-13T10:36:51.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201213/6BLPQA7E3ZCNVBVPIKZPOQSUII/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201213%2F6BLPQA7E3ZCNVBVPIKZPOQSUII%2F&d=S6zCjV1yqQRAjAhc4t20mbM5QgR%2FpIHXQ%2BfAgFWVWJ0%3D&h=3b1da84d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201213%2F6BLPQA7E3ZCNVBVPIKZPOQSUII%2F&h=ec65d3cc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201213/6BLPQA7E3ZCNVBVPIKZPOQSUII/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n警阻靠近「送車師」照追嗌加油<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/RY_vMtM4p32fg27TU8DTmjUQCBY=/1000x624/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/2WCKK2PVTJDJLB7X7UDX4YXX4Q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FRY_vMtM4p32fg27TU8DTmjUQCBY%3D%2F1000x624%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F2WCKK2PVTJDJLB7X7UDX4YXX4Q.jpg&h=efaadfaf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■「王婆婆」走到囚車出口處叫口號，遭數名警員抬回行人路。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】黎智英提堂程序完結後，大批支持者化身「送車師」，在西九龍裁判法院外的通州街等候黎智英的囚車離開。警方在囚車駛經的馬路設起膠帶防止支持者走近，他們惟有隔着囚車的鐵窗高叫「黎生，加油！保重呀！」<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：鐵鏈纏腰押解 黎從容手比愛心<br />\n<br />\n囚車昨早約8時10分抵達法院，庭外有數十名警員佈防及封路。<br />\n<br />\n有人帶備標語和物件，希望黎。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：警列美政策無解釋與黎關係  大狀質疑「乜都入佢數」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n支持者繪標語聲援<br />\n<br />\n唐小姐亦親自繪畫一張「肥佬黎撐住」標語，旁邊還畫上一顆蘋果。她說現身支持因現況「唔公平」，對黎的狀況感擔心，「國安法係一個好大嘅窿，講乜都可以塞到入去」，是次加控明顯是「老屈」，只為打壓異己。<br />\n<br />\n「王婆婆」王鳳瑤亦手持黃傘。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n過往當有抗爭者被囚車押走，總有一群「送車師」追着囚車向被告打氣，警方昨為阻止支持者走近囚車，早在馬路旁拉膠帶，又派駐大量警力佈防。當載着黎智英的囚車駛出，支持者惟有在行人路上高聲說「黎生，加油！保重呀！」雖未能走近，有人仍然追着囚車向黎打氣，直至囚車遠去。"},{"pid":"3c22818b83d11cb05010a235fdd14de55766e0de","tid":2323661,"uid":12232,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-13T12:17:43.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b882e8bd22327764b904bf21f5a46aaac2849de7","tid":2323661,"uid":58841,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-13T12:30:20.000Z","msg":"嗌加油都唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}